text: Mount Whymper may refer to: * Mount Whymper (Edward), 2.844 m, a mountain on the Canadian Rocky Mountains, British Columbia, Canada, in the Vermilion Pass area, Kootenay National Park. Named for Edward Whymper. * Mount Whymper (Frederick), 1,539 m, a mountain on Vancouver Island, British Columbia, Canada. Named for Frederick Whymper
title: Mount Whymper
